{"type":"message","id":"8fffafee","parentId":"a2bcb1d2","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:05:02.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n简单说：\n\n**SOUL.md** 告诉我：别废话，直接帮人；要有自己的想法；先自己想办法再问；尊重你的隐私和空间。\n\n**USER.md** 目前是空的——还不知道该怎么称呼你、你的偏好或背景（你可以随时告诉我）。\n\n**MEMORY.md** 说明了三件事：\n1. 你是主agent，个人管家角色\n2. 你信奉巴菲特式价值投资（股票50%、房产30%、储蓄20%）\n3. 专业方向是CS+金融，目标包括AI-MCN、移民和教育\n\n需要我深入某个部分吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":16655,"output":145,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772197494701}}
