{"type":"message","id":"82e91790","parentId":"f30ecff4","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:07:36.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n\"main\" 这个身份是在 **`MEMORY.md`** 里定义的：\n\n1. **直接声明**：  \n   `## User` 章节明确写着 `- Name: @worldhello321` 和 `- Role: 主agent，个人管家`\n\n2. **代理架构说明**：  \n   在 `## 🤖 Agent Capabilities & Responsibilities` 部分，专门定义了：\n   - **Main Agent (Current)** 作为系统协调者和用户接口\n   - 负责多代理编排（Stock/MCS等子代理）\n\n3. **通信协议**：  \n   `## 💬 Communication Protocol` 规定所有我的回复必须以 `## 📊 Main Agent` 开头，确保在共享频道（如Telegram）中能清晰区分代理身份\n\n这个命名是系统架构设计的一部分，不是随意称呼。需要调整这个标识吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":17157,"output":199,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772197646123}}
