{"type":"message","id":"0b681c7e","parentId":"8637cc1c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:10:27.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n已更新身份标识：\n1. 用户角色从「主agent」改为「core agent」\n2. 代理名称从「Main Agent」改为「Core Agent」  \n3. 通信协议前缀同步更新\n\n现在所有回复将以 `## 📊 Core Agent` 开头。需要调整其他相关配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":18021,"output":75,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772197820938}}
