{"type":"message","id":"00b16266","parentId":"4925f62c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:11:10.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n目前系统配置**不允许直接启动 Stock Agent**。根据权限检查：\n- 可用的子代理只有 `main`（当前会话）\n- `stock` 代理未在允许列表中\n\n可能的原因：\n1. Stock Agent 需要通过其他方式激活（如特定触发条件）\n2. 系统配置需要更新以启用多代理功能\n\n建议操作：\n- 检查 `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/config.json` 中的 `subagents` 配置\n- 或运行 `openclaw status` 查看当前代理状态\n\n需要我帮你诊断具体配置问题吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":18340,"output":140,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18480,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772197865399}}
{"type":"message","id":"978c8939","parentId":"00b16266","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:14:14.816Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 21:14 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n如果我希望完全独立的agent，相互协调工作，而且互相通过telegram通讯的话，最好的办法是什么"}],"timestamp":1772198054815}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae3e4a99","parentId":"978c8939","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:14:28.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n要实现**完全独立的多代理系统**并通过 Telegram 协作，最佳方案是：\n\n### 1. **每个代理作为独立 OpenClaw 实例运行**\n- 为每个代理（core/stock/mcs）创建**独立的 workspace 目录**\n- 每个实例配置**专属的 Telegram bot token**（或使用不同用户账号）\n- 通过 `openclaw gateway start --workspace /path/to/agent-workspace` 分别启动\n\n### 2. **代理间通信协议**\n- **直接消息**：每个代理知道其他代理的 Telegram chat_id\n  ```bash\n  # stock agent 发送消息给 core\n  openclaw message send --to \"telegram:YOUR_CORE_CHAT_ID\" --message \"持仓更新完成\"\n  ```\n- **标准化消息格式**：约定 JSON 格式传递结构化数据\n  ```json\n  {\"from\":\"stock\",\"action\":\"portfolio_update\",\"data\":{...}}\n  ```\n\n### 3. **关键配置文件调整**\n```yaml\n# 每个代理的 config.json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"token\": \"AGENT_SPECIFIC_BOT_TOKEN\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"enabled\": false  # 禁用子代理模式，保持完全独立\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. **协调机制**\n- **核心代理（core）** 作为调度中心，接收用户指令后向其他代理发送任务\n- **事件驱动**：通过 Telegram 消息触发代理行为（如收到特定关键词时执行操作）\n- **状态同步**：每个代理定期向 core 发送心跳消息\n\n> 💡 这种架构避免了权限限制问题，每个代理拥有完整自主权，同时通过 Telegram 实现松耦合协作。\n\n需要我帮你搭建其中一个代理的初始配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":18552,"output":403,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18955,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772198054816}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac81d08b","parentId":"ae3e4a99","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:16:02.685Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 21:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n在同一个openclaw实例中，多个agent方案是不可靠的吗"}],"timestamp":1772198162684}}
{"type":"message","id":"a63484bd","parentId":"ac81d08b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:16:17.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**同一个 OpenClaw 实例的多代理方案不是不可靠，而是有明确的能力边界**：\n\n### ✅ **适合场景**\n- **轻量级任务分发**（如：core 接收请求 → 调用 stock 计算 → 返回结果）\n- **共享内存/文件系统**的紧密协作（通过 `MEMORY.md` 和 workspace 文件协调）\n- **单通道输出**（所有代理共用一个 Telegram 会话，靠前缀区分身份）\n\n### ⚠️ **关键限制**\n1. **权限隔离弱**  \n   所有代理共享同一进程权限，无法实现真正的安全沙箱\n   \n2. **通信依赖内部机制**  \n   代理间通过 `sessions_send` 通信，**不经过 Telegram**（与你要求的「通过 Telegram 通讯」冲突）\n\n3. **故障传播风险**  \n   一个代理崩溃可能导致整个实例不稳定\n\n4. **当前配置限制**  \n   你的系统已禁用子代理创建（`agents_list` 显示只有 main 可用）\n\n### 🔧 **折中方案**\n如果坚持单实例：\n- 用 **独立线程会话** 模拟多代理（`sessions_spawn` + `thread:true`）\n- 但需**手动实现 Telegram 中继**（每个「代理」收到内部消息后主动发送 Telegram 消息）\n\n> 💡 结论：若需要**真正的独立性+Telegram 原生通信**，多实例是更干净的方案。单实例适合简单任务路由，不适合复杂代理协作。\n\n需要我演示具体配置差异吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":19022,"output":348,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19370,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772198162685}}
{"type":"message","id":"a835f690","parentId":"a63484bd","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:17:39.984Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 21:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n那么如果我在同一台电脑启动多个openclaw做好的方式是docker吗"}],"timestamp":1772198259982}}
{"type":"message","id":"665316f8","parentId":"a835f690","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:18:02.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**Docker 不是必须的，但能解决关键痛点**。以下是两种方案对比：\n\n### 🐳 **Docker 方案（推荐）**\n```bash\n# 为每个代理创建独立容器\ndocker run -d \\\n  -v /path/to/core-workspace:/root/.openclaw \\\n  -e TELEGRAM_TOKEN=\"CORE_BOT_TOKEN\" \\\n  openclaw:latest\n\ndocker run -d \\\n  -v /path/to/stock-workspace:/root/.openclaw \\\n  -e TELEGRAM_TOKEN=\"STOCK_BOT_TOKEN\" \\\n  openclaw:latest\n```\n\n**优势**：\n- ✅ 完全进程隔离（崩溃互不影响）\n- ✅ 独立依赖环境（不同代理可使用不同 OpenClaw 版本）\n- ✅ 资源限制（CPU/内存配额）\n- ✅ 一键启停（`docker-compose up/down`）\n\n**劣势**：\n- 需要维护 Docker 镜像\n- 文件系统隔离需显式挂载\n\n### 💻 **原生多进程方案**\n```bash\n# 终端1\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace ~/.openclaw/agents/core\n\n# 终端2  \nopenclaw gateway start --workspace ~/.openclaw/agents/stock\n```\n\n**优势**：\n- 无需额外技术栈\n- 直接访问主机文件系统\n\n**劣势**：\n- ❌ 共享 Node.js 环境（版本冲突风险）\n- ❌ 需手动管理进程（nohup/systemd）\n- ❌ 无资源隔离\n\n### 🔧 **关键配置**\n无论哪种方案，每个代理的 `config.json` 必须包含：\n```json\n{\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 3001  // 每个实例不同端口\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"token\": \"AGENT_SPECIFIC_TOKEN\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n> 💡 **建议**：如果追求稳定性 → 选 Docker；如果快速验证 → 用原生多进程。需要我提供具体的 `docker-compose.yml` 模板吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":19438,"output":477,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19915,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772198259983}}
{"type":"message","id":"86f9df5b","parentId":"665316f8","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:19:20.878Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 21:19 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n你的意思是我只需要启动多个openclaw的gateway就是多个实例了么？"}],"timestamp":1772198360877}}
{"type":"message","id":"08f96baa","parentId":"86f9df5b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:19:32.554Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**是的，完全正确**。你只需要：\n\n```bash\n# 每个命令启动一个独立实例\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace /path/to/agent1-workspace\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace /path/to/agent2-workspace\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace /path/to/agent3-workspace\n```\n\n### 关键要求：\n1. **每个实例必须有独立的 workspace 目录**  \n   （包含各自的 `config.json`、`MEMORY.md`、会话记录等）\n\n2. **每个实例的 `config.json` 必须配置不同端口**  \n   ```json\n   {\n     \"gateway\": {\n       \"port\": 3001  // agent1\n     }\n   }\n   ```\n\n3. **每个实例绑定不同的 Telegram 身份**  \n   - 方案A：不同 bot token（需创建多个 Telegram bot）\n   - 方案B：同一账号但不同 chat_id（通过消息过滤区分）\n\n### 验证是否成功：\n```bash\n# 查看所有实例进程\nps aux | grep \"openclaw gateway\"\n\n# 检查端口占用\nlsof -i :3001\nlsof -i :3002\n```\n\n> 💡 这就是最轻量级的多代理实现——**不需要 Docker，不需要复杂配置**，OpenClaw 原生支持多实例。每个实例都是完全独立的进程，崩溃互不影响。\n\n需要我帮你生成具体的 workspace 目录结构模板吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":19983,"output":339,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772198360878}}
