{"type":"message","id":"36336658","parentId":"f3679680","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:45:47.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**实际上提交是成功的！** 让我澄清一下：\n\n### ✅ 确认成功状态\n- **本地 Git 状态**: `working tree clean`（无未提交更改）\n- **提交历史**: \n  - `49f9d05` - 重构项目结构（最新）\n  - `52b807b` - 初始提交\n- **文件结构**: 完全符合你的要求\n  ```\n  ai-note/\n  ├── README.md                 # AI托管记事本介绍\n  ├── index.md                  # 全局索引\n  └── openclaw/\n      └── proxy-solutions.md    # OpenClaw代理解决方案\n  ```\n\n### 🔍 为什么你觉得失败了？\nGitHub API 限流导致我无法通过 API 验证远程仓库内容，但**本地 Git 日志明确显示推送成功**：\n```\nTo https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note.git\n   52b807b..49f9d05  main -> main\n```\n\n### 🧪 手动验证\n你可以直接访问：\n- **项目主页**: https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note\n- **OpenClaw文档**: https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note/blob/main/openclaw/proxy-solutions.md\n\n所有文件都已正确上传并按你的要求组织。这是一个完全AI友好的技术文档库，其他AI系统可以直接引用这些结构化内容。\n\n需要我做任何调整吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":43336,"output":337,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772199936193}}
