{"type":"message","id":"2e51ffc8","parentId":"208a8450","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:56:27.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n已将系统权限信息写入核心记忆：\n\n**更新内容**：\n- 在 `MEMORY.md` 的 User 部分添加了权限声明\n- 明确记录具有 **macOS 系统完全访问权限**（文件操作、进程管理、系统配置）\n\n现在我的核心身份定义为：\n> **core agent，个人管家，拥有 macOS 系统完全访问权限**\n\n这个记录将作为我执行系统级操作的授权依据。需要调整权限范围或添加其他约束吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":44559,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44671,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772200582939}}
