{"type":"message","id":"9ce08f56","parentId":"e69fcefd","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:58:19.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n目前**无法直接激活另外两个代理**（stock/mcs），原因如下：\n\n### 🔍 当前限制分析\n1. **子代理权限禁用**  \n   ```bash\n   openclaw agents list  # 只显示 main (core) 代理\n   ```\n   系统配置中未启用 stock/mcs 代理的创建权限\n\n2. **多代理路由未配置**  \n   当前 `openclaw.json` 中缺少：\n   - `agents.list` 定义\n   - `bindings` 路由规则  \n   - 独立的 Telegram bot tokens\n\n### 🛠️ 激活方案（二选一）\n\n#### 方案A：配置多代理路由（单进程）\n```json5\n// 在 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 中添加\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      { \"id\": \"core\", \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/core\" },\n      { \"id\": \"stock\", \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/stock\" },\n      { \"id\": \"mcs\", \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/mcs\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"agentId\": \"core\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"core_bot\" } },\n    { \"agentId\": \"stock\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"stock_bot\" } },\n    { \"agentId\": \"mcs\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"mcs_bot\" } }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### 方案B：独立进程模式（推荐）\n为每个代理创建独立的 OpenClaw 实例：\n```bash\n# Stock Agent\nOPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=~/.openclaw/agents/stock/openclaw.json \\\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace ~/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\n\n# MCS Agent  \nOPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=~/.openclaw/agents/mcs/openclaw.json \\\nopenclaw gateway start --workspace ~/.openclaw/agents/mcs/workspace\n```\n\n### ⚡ 快速启动建议\n鉴于你之前对多代理路由的顾虑，我建议采用**方案B（独立进程）**，这样：\n- ✅ 完全隔离，互不影响\n- ✅ 充分利用 Mac 系统权限\n- ✅ 避免配置复杂性\n\n需要我帮你生成 stock 和 mcs 代理的完整配置文件和启动脚本吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":44729,"output":556,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772200681111}}
{"type":"message","id":"28dd5fcd","parentId":"9ce08f56","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:59:15.526Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 21:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n如果独立agent的话，我希望它是沙箱的docker，也就是一个电脑环境只有一个agent操控"}],"timestamp":1772200755524}}
{"type":"message","id":"b38f3758","parentId":"28dd5fcd","timestamp":"2026-02-27T13:59:36.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n完全理解你的需求。**每个代理 = 独立 Docker 容器 + 专属 macOS 权限** 是最安全的架构。\n\n### 🐳 最终方案：Docker 沙箱 + macOS 集成\n\n虽然 Docker 在 macOS 有局限，但我们可以通过**精心配置**实现最佳平衡：\n\n#### 1. **容器配置策略**\n```yaml\n# docker-compose.yml\nversion: '3.8'\nservices:\n  core-agent:\n    image: openclaw:latest\n    volumes:\n      # 必需的 macOS 集成\n      - ~/.openclaw/agents/core:/root/.openclaw\n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock  # 容器内 Docker 支持\n    environment:\n      - TELEGRAM_TOKEN=${CORE_TELEGRAM_TOKEN}\n    network_mode: host  # 直接使用主机网络（解决代理问题）\n\n  stock-agent:\n    image: openclaw:latest  \n    volumes:\n      - ~/.openclaw/agents/stock:/root/.openclaw\n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock\n    environment:\n      - TELEGRAM_TOKEN=${STOCK_TELEGRAM_TOKEN}\n    network_mode: host\n\n  mcs-agent:\n    image: openclaw:latest\n    volumes:\n      - ~/.openclaw/agents/mcs:/root/.openclaw  \n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock\n    environment:\n      - TELEGRAM_TOKEN=${MCS_TELEGRAM_TOKEN}\n    network_mode: host\n```\n\n#### 2. **macOS 特定优化**\n- **网络模式**: `host` 模式确保代理配置正常工作\n- **文件系统**: 只挂载必要的 OpenClaw workspace 目录\n- **权限控制**: 每个容器只能访问自己的 workspace\n\n#### 3. **启动脚本**\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动所有代理\ndocker-compose up -d\n\n# 验证状态\ndocker-compose ps\n```\n\n### ⚠️ 关键限制说明\n- **Apple 原生工具**: `remindctl`, `memo`, `imsg` 等仍无法在容器内使用\n- **硬件访问**: 摄像头/麦克风需要额外配置（通常不推荐）\n- **性能**: 文件 I/O 比原生稍慢，但可接受\n\n### ✅ 这样做的优势\n- **完全隔离**: 每个代理运行在独立容器中\n- **安全沙箱**: 一个代理崩溃不影响其他代理\n- **配置简单**: 通过 docker-compose 统一管理\n- **网络兼容**: host 网络模式确保代理正常工作\n\n需要我生成完整的 `docker-compose.yml` 和配套的配置文件模板吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":45355,"output":612,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45967,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772200755525}}
