{"type":"message","id":"ae2d35fd","parentId":"a7cfe8e9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:02:57.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **完整方案已提交到 AI-Note 项目！**\n\n### 📁 新增文档\n- **架构方案**: [`architecture/openclaw-multi-agent.md`](https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note/blob/main/architecture/openclaw-multi-agent.md)\n- **索引更新**: `index.md` 已包含新文档链接\n\n### 🎯 方案核心要点\n1. **推荐 Docker 沙箱方案** - 安全隔离优先\n2. **三个代理角色明确定义** - Core/Stock/MCS 各司其职  \n3. **Telegram 通信协议** - 独立 bot + 标准化消息格式\n4. **权限最小化** - Core 拥有完整权限，其他代理受限\n5. **实施路线图** - 分四个阶段逐步实现\n\n### 🔗 项目状态\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note\n- **核心记忆**: 已记录 AI-Note 项目位置和用途\n- **权限声明**: Core Agent 的 macOS 完全访问权限已写入 MEMORY.md\n\n这个方案为你的多代理系统提供了清晰的技术路线，既保证了安全性，又保持了 macOS 兼容性。需要我开始实施第一阶段（基础架构搭建）吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":48551,"output":288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772200967056}}
