{"type":"message","id":"fcd195ae","parentId":"f183a336","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:24:37.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **群聊配置方案已形成并记录**\n\n### 📝 方案文档\n**文件位置**: `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/openclaw/solutions/telegram-group-chat.md`\n\n**方案内容**:\n```markdown\n# OpenClaw Telegram 群聊配置方案\n\n## 目标\n启用 Core Agent 在 Telegram 群组中的消息接收和回复能力，同时保持适当的响应策略。\n\n## 配置选项\n\n### 选项A: 安全模式（推荐）\n- **行为**: 仅响应明确 @core 的消息\n- **配置**:\n  ```json5\n  {\n    \"channels\": {\n      \"telegram\": {\n        \"groups\": {\n          \"*\": {\n            \"allow\": true,\n            \"requireMention\": true,\n            \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@core\", \"core\"]\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  ```\n\n### 选项B: 活跃模式  \n- **行为**: 响应群组中所有消息\n- **配置**:\n  ```json5\n  {\n    \"channels\": {\n      \"telegram\": {\n        \"groups\": {\n          \"GROUP_ID_HERE\": {\n            \"allow\": true,\n            \"requireMention\": false\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  ```\n\n## 实施步骤\n\n1. **备份当前配置**\n   ```bash\n   cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.backup\n   ```\n\n2. **获取群组ID**（如使用选项B）\n   - 临时启用调试模式获取群组ID\n   - 或通过 Telegram API 查询\n\n3. **应用配置**\n   - 将选定配置合并到现有 `openclaw.json`\n   - 确保 JSON5 语法正确\n\n4. **验证配置**\n   ```bash\n   openclaw doctor  # 检查配置有效性\n   ```\n\n5. **重启服务**\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n\n6. **测试功能**\n   - 在目标群组中发送 @core 测试消息\n   - 验证响应是否正常\n\n## 回滚计划\n\n如启动失败：\n1. **恢复备份配置**\n   ```bash\n   cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.backup ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n   ```\n2. **重启服务**\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n\n## 风险评估\n\n- **低风险**: 选项A（安全模式）几乎不会导致启动失败\n- **中风险**: 选项B需要正确的群组ID，错误ID可能导致警告但不影响启动\n- **防护措施**: 配置备份 + `openclaw doctor` 预验证\n\n---\n**文档类型**: 配置方案  \n**适用场景**: OpenClaw Telegram 群聊集成  \n**最后更新**: 2026-02-27\n```\n\n### 🔗 项目更新\n- **已添加到 AI-Note**: https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note/blob/main/openclaw/solutions/telegram-group-chat.md\n- **索引已更新**: `index.md` 包含新文档链接\n\n这个方案包含了完整的实施步骤、风险评估和回滚计划，确保安全地启用群聊功能。当你准备执行时，我可以按这个方案逐步操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":51642,"output":732,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52374,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772202249286}}
