{"type":"message","id":"1598c35c","parentId":"26b89b8c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:24:51.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a052f8aa95f249fba2838627","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":52436,"output":35,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52471,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772202287578}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad256b8b","parentId":"1598c35c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:24:51.332Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a052f8aa95f249fba2838627","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Quick Checks\n\n## Checks (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **Memory**: Important decisions → `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` + `MEMORY.md`\n- [ ] **SQLite**: If memory updated → run `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- [ ] **Backup**: If changes → run `backup.sh`\n\n## Scripts\n```bash\n./check-memory.sh              # Create today's log\n./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh  # Update search index\n./backup.sh                    # Commit & push\n```\n\n## When to Reach Out\n- Important emails\n- Calendar event < 2h\n- Found something interesting\n- Been > 8h since last message\n\n## Stay Quiet (HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- Late night (23:00-08:00)\n- Human busy\n- Nothing new\n- Checked < 30 min ago\n\n---\n*Last check: 2026-02-24 22:00*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772202291328}}
{"type":"message","id":"b456e236","parentId":"ad256b8b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:25:02.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n根据 `HEARTBEAT.md` 文件，**当前没有设置固定的 heartbeat 间隔**。\n\n### 🔍 现状分析\n- **最后检查**: 2026-02-24 22:00（3天前）\n- **触发条件**: 基于事件驱动，而非定时执行\n  - 重要邮件\n  - 日历事件 < 2小时  \n  - 发现有趣内容\n  - 超过8小时无消息\n\n### ⏰ 协调器 Heartbeat 配置\n但在 `MEMORY.md` 中定义了**协调器专用的 heartbeat**：\n- **频率**: 每2小时一次（8:00, 10:00, 12:00, 14:00, 16:00, 18:00, 20:00）\n- **静默期**: 22:00 - 8:00（不执行）\n- **目的**: 纯粹的系统健康监控\n\n### 💡 建议\n如果你希望更频繁的主动检查，可以：\n1. **调整协调器频率**（比如每小时一次）\n2. **启用常规 heartbeat**（在 HEARTBEAT.md 中设置固定间隔）\n\n需要我帮你修改 heartbeat 配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":52706,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53003,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772202291333}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb872613","parentId":"b456e236","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:27:57.191Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 22:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n每天工作日志总结调整到23点55分，然后总结内容里去掉协调其他子agent进行工作日志总结的动作，调整memory.md"}],"timestamp":1772202477189}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe7d8d58","parentId":"bb872613","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:28:18.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a08dd99b946448b9826df0d8","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/MEMORY.md","oldText":"## 📅 Daily Backup Process (22:00)\nWhen receiving \"执行每日备份\" system event at 22:00, Main Agent must coordinate the following workflow:\n\n### Phase 1: Agent Self-Summary (22:00)\n- **Stock Agent**: Generate daily investment summary, write to `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`, execute `sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- **MCS Agent**: Generate daily career development summary, write to `agents/mcs/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`, execute `sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- **Main Agent**: Wait for confirmation that both agents have completed their summaries\n\n### Phase 2: Main Agent Summary (22:05)\n- **Main Agent**: Generate system coordination summary from session transcripts (`agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`) and system activity logs, write to `agents/main/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **Main Agent**: Execute `./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` to update main memory index\n- **Validation**: Ensure all three agents have valid daily log entries for the date\n\n### Phase 3: GitHub Backup (22:10)\n- **Execute**: `./backup.sh` to commit all changes to GitHub repository\n- **Include**: All MEMORY.md files, daily logs, session transcripts, and system configurations\n- **Verification**: Confirm successful push to remote repository\n\n### Key Principles\n- **Agent Autonomy**: Each agent maintains its own memory system independently\n- **Coordination**: Main Agent orchestrates the backup process but does not generate agent content\n- **Completeness**: All daily activities are captured in respective agent memory systems\n- **Reliability**: Automated backup ensures no data loss","newText":"## 📅 Daily Backup Process (23:55)\nWhen receiving \"执行每日备份\" system event at 23:55, Core Agent must execute the following workflow:\n\n### Phase 1: Core Agent Daily Summary (23:55)\n- **Core Agent**: Generate daily system summary from session transcripts (`agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`) and system activity logs, write to `agents/main/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **Core Agent**: Execute `./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` to update main memory index\n\n### Phase 2: GitHub Backup (24:00)\n- **Execute**: `./backup.sh` to commit all changes to GitHub repository\n- **Include**: MEMORY.md files, daily logs, session transcripts, and system configurations\n- **Verification**: Confirm successful push to remote repository\n\n### Key Principles\n- **Autonomy**: Core Agent maintains its own memory system independently\n- **Simplicity**: No coordination with other agents required\n- **Reliability**: Automated backup ensures no data loss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":53087,"output":630,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772202477191}}
