{"type":"message","id":"f4e02ab2","parentId":"0e0638b5","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:28:25.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **Daily Backup Process 已成功调整**\n\n### 📝 主要变更\n1. **时间调整**: 从 22:00 → **23:55**\n2. **流程简化**: \n   - 移除了协调 Stock/MCS Agent 的步骤\n   - Core Agent 只负责自己的日志总结\n3. **角色更新**: Main Agent → **Core Agent**\n4. **原则更新**: 强调自主性和简洁性\n\n### 🔧 新的备份流程\n- **23:55**: Core Agent 生成自己的日志总结\n- **24:00**: 执行 GitHub 备份\n\n现在我的每日总结完全独立，不再依赖其他代理的协作。这个配置更符合你希望的简化架构。\n\n需要调整其他相关配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":53752,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772202498823}}
