{"type":"message","id":"47162c89","parentId":"4a4508a6","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:43:59.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n我**不会自动加载 README.md 文件**。\n\n### 📖 我的启动加载流程\n根据 `AGENTS.md` 的 Session Checklist，我只在启动时加载以下文件：\n1. **`SOUL.md`** - 人格和行为准则\n2. **`USER.md`** - 关于你的基本信息  \n3. **`MEMORY.md`** - 系统配置和长期记忆\n4. **当日/昨日的日志文件** - `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n### 📄 README.md 的处理方式\n- **不会自动读取**: README.md 被视为项目文档，不是系统配置\n- **按需加载**: 只有当你明确要求我读取或操作 README.md 时才会加载\n- **工作区无关**: 即使 README.md 在我的工作区目录中，也不会自动加载\n\n### 💡 为什么这样设计\n- **性能考虑**: 避免加载不必要的文件\n- **职责分离**: README 是给人看的文档，不是给 AI 的配置\n- **按需原则**: 只加载对当前任务必要的信息\n\n如果你希望我在启动时加载特定的 README 文件，请告诉我具体路径，我可以将其纳入启动流程。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":56273,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56536,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772203423398}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9964181","parentId":"47162c89","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:44:36.909Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-02-27 22:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n写一个.openclaw目录的readme.md放到其目录里"}],"timestamp":1772203476907}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff6b87f9","parentId":"d9964181","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:44:59.347Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4a42871e46294f6cbc2e690d","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/README.md","content":"# OpenClaw Agent Runtime Directory\n\nThis directory contains the complete runtime environment for OpenClaw AI agents.\n\n## Directory Structure\n\n```\n.openclaw/\n├── agents/                 # Individual agent workspaces and state\n│   └── main/              # Core agent workspace (current)\n│       └── workspace/     # Core agent's working directory\n├── workspace/             # Global shared workspace\n├── memory/                # Memory system and SQLite search index\n├── cron/                  # Scheduled job configurations\n├── credentials/           # Channel authentication credentials\n├── logs/                  # System and agent activity logs\n├── telegram/              # Telegram channel data\n├── devices/               # Paired device information\n├── mem0/                  # Vector memory storage\n├── browser/               # Browser automation cache\n├── canvas/                # Canvas UI rendering data\n├── identity/              # Agent identity configurations\n├── completions/           # Auto-completion caches\n├── subagents/             # Sub-agent runtime data\n├── delivery-queue/        # Message delivery queue\n├── openclaw.json          # Main configuration file\n├── config.yaml            # Auxiliary configuration\n├── gateway.env            # Gateway environment variables\n├── exec-approvals.json    # Execution approval records\n└── update-check.json      # Update check metadata\n```\n\n## Key Components\n\n### Agents\n- **Core Agent**: Located at `agents/main/workspace`\n- **Role**: System coordinator, user interface, multi-agent orchestration\n- **Permissions**: Full macOS system access\n\n### Memory System\n- **Long-term**: `MEMORY.md` - Curated knowledge and system configuration\n- **Daily logs**: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - Raw activity logs\n- **Search index**: SQLite database for semantic memory retrieval\n\n### Configuration\n- **Primary**: `openclaw.json` - Main configuration with channel tokens and agent settings\n- **Backup**: Multiple `.bak` versions maintained automatically\n- **Environment**: `gateway.env` - Runtime environment variables\n\n### Security\n- **Credentials**: Stored in `credentials/` directory with restricted permissions\n- **Execution approvals**: Recorded in `exec-approvals.json`\n- **Isolation**: Each agent maintains separate workspace and state\n\n## Usage Guidelines\n\n- **Do not manually modify** files in this directory unless you understand the implications\n- **Backup regularly**: The system automatically backs up configuration files\n- **Agent autonomy**: Each agent manages its own workspace independently\n- **Memory persistence**: Important decisions should be recorded in MEMORY.md or daily logs\n\n## Related Projects\n\n- **AI-Note**: [https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note](https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note)\n  - AI-friendly technical documentation repository\n  - Contains OpenClaw architecture and solution guides\n\n---\n**Generated**: 2026-02-27  \n**Agent**: core  \n**Host**: hope's Mac mini"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":56601,"output":658,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57259,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772203476909}}
