{"type":"message","id":"4e223150","parentId":"0e14b6e3","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:47:45.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_53ef6de808714bbc88f4db3f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/README.md","content":"# Core Agent Workspace\n\nThis is the working directory for the **Core Agent**, serving as the main system coordinator and user interface.\n\n## Directory Purpose\n\n- **File operations**: All file reads/writes happen in this directory unless specified otherwise\n- **Session workspace**: Current session's temporary files and outputs\n- **Agent-specific storage**: Core Agent's personal files and configurations\n\n## Key Files\n\n- **`MEMORY.md`**: Long-term memory and system configuration\n- **`SOUL.md`**: Core Agent personality and behavioral guidelines  \n- **`USER.md`**: Information about the human user being assisted\n- **`TOOLS.md`**: Environment-specific tool configurations and notes\n- **`IDENTITY.md`**: Agent identity definition (name, avatar, etc.)\n- **`HEARTBEAT.md`**: System health check protocols and schedules\n\n## Memory System\n\n- **Daily logs**: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - Raw session transcripts and activities\n- **Long-term memory**: `MEMORY.md` - Curated knowledge and important decisions\n- **Search index**: SQLite database in `memory-index/` for semantic retrieval\n\n## Agent Capabilities\n\n- **System coordination**: Manages overall OpenClaw system health\n- **User interface**: Primary point of contact for user interactions  \n- **Multi-agent orchestration**: Coordinates with other specialized agents when needed\n- **Full macOS permissions**: Complete access to file system, processes, and system configuration\n\n## Related Directories\n\n- **OpenClaw root**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/` - Complete runtime environment\n- **AI-Note project**: `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/` - Technical documentation repository\n\n---\n**Workspace**: Core Agent  \n**Host**: hope's Mac mini  \n**Last Updated**: 2026-02-27"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":58468,"output":418,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58886,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772203651228}}
