{"type":"message","id":"54c3e276","parentId":"66e911bb","timestamp":"2026-02-27T14:52:40.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dec4955d814247aab9e4ef32","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/USER.md","oldText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n*Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go.*\n\n- **Name:** Andy Tien (@Linux2010)\n- **What to call them:** Andy\n- **Pronouns:** he/him\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Location:** Shanghai, China\n- **Company:** Ant Group\n- **Bio:** Java | Python | Bigdata | Data Warehouse | Data Analysis | AI\n\n## Context\n\n**Technical Focus:**\n- Backend development (Java/Python)\n- Big data and data warehouse systems  \n- AI/ML integration and applications\n- Open source contributions (147 public repos)\n\n**Current Projects:**\n- **The ONE**: Personal framework combining CS+Fin expertise with AI-MCN goals\n- **AI-Note**: AI-friendly technical documentation repository\n- **OpenClaw Multi-Agent System**: Core/Stock/MCS agent architecture\n\n**Professional Background:**\n- Works at Ant Group (major Chinese fintech company)\n- Active GitHub contributor since 2018\n- Strong focus on data engineering and AI systems\n\n**Interests & Goals:**\n- Value investing (Buffett follower) with SPY/QQQ portfolio\n- Computer Science certification and career development  \n- AI-MCN (AI Multi-Channel Network) creation\n- Immigration and education planning\n\n**Communication Style:**\n- Direct and technical\n- Prefers structured solutions over casual conversation\n- Values efficiency and precision in responses\n\n---\n\nThe more I know, the better I can help. But remember — I'm learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.","newText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n*Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go.*\n\n- **Name:** Andy Tien (@Linux2010)\n- **What to call them:** Andy\n- **Pronouns:** he/him\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Location:** Shanghai, China\n- **Company:** Ant Group\n- **Bio:** Java | Python | Bigdata | Data Warehouse | Data Analysis | AI\n\n## Context\n\n**The ONE Framework (人生三大支柱):**\n- **价值(50%)**: 健康家庭 + 资产配置（股票50%:SPY40+QQQ40+趋势20 / 房产30% / 储蓄20%）\n- **专业(30%)**: CS认证(MCS) + 金融硕士(MFin) \n- **希望(20%)**: AI-MCN + 移民教育 + 自动化创业\n\n**Investment Philosophy:**\n- 巴菲特信徒，价值投资践行者\n- 严格纪律：不融资/不做空/不碰衍生品\n- 耐心持有，敬畏市场，跟随市场\n\n**Professional Development:**\n- **CS Certifications**: OceanBase/TDSQL/麒麟/PMP已获，雅思7分/MBA/FRM进行中\n- **Work Experience**: 蚂蚁集团、宇信、苏银消金等金融科技公司\n- **Technical Stack**: Java/Python/Bigdata/AI系统架构\n\n**AI-MCN Vision:**\n- **Hope-AI系统**: 自动化内容生成矩阵（YouTube/B站/头条）\n- **Current Status**: 维护B站月入1k，升级为AI驱动原创内容\n- **Methodology**: 本地大模型 + Prompt工程 + 分布式任务调度\n\n**Core Principles:**\n- **表达公式**: what-why-how + 观点+理由+案例+结论\n- **行动原则**: 5秒立即投入法\n- **社交理念**: 让人如沐春风，不在意他人眼光\n\n---\n\nThe more I know, the better I can help. But remember — I'm learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":65466,"output":869,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66335,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772203931029}}
