y**: 本地大模型 + Prompt工程 + 分布式任务调度\n 36 \n-37 **Communication Style:**\n-38 - Direct and technical\n-39 - Prefers structured solutions over casual conversation\n-40 - Values efficiency and precision in responses\n+35 **Core Principles:**\n+36 - **表达公式**: what-why-how + 观点+理由+案例+结论\n+37 - **行动原则**: 5秒立即投入法\n+38 - **社交理念**: 让人如沐春风，不在意他人眼光\n 41 \n 42 ---\n 43 \n 44 The more I know, the better I can help. But remember — I'm learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.","firstChangedLine":15},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772203960392}}
