{"type":"message","id":"00aaf478","parentId":"4046c5cf","timestamp":"2026-02-27T15:16:36.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**构建官方 OpenClaw Docker 镜像遇到问题**，主要原因是：\n\n### 🔍 问题分析\n1. **NPM 安装缺少 Dockerfile**: 通过 `npm install -g openclaw` 安装的版本不包含 Docker 构建文件\n2. **GitHub 克隆超时**: 网络问题导致无法完整克隆仓库\n3. **临时目录权限**: macOS 的 `/tmp` 目录有特殊权限限制\n\n### 🛠️ 解决方案\n\n#### 方案A: 使用官方预构建镜像（推荐）\n```bash\n# 拉取官方镜像（如果存在）\ndocker pull ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:latest\n```\n\n#### 方案B: 手动创建简化 Dockerfile\n```dockerfile\n# 创建 /tmp/openclaw-docker/Dockerfile\nFROM node:22-bookworm\n\nRUN corepack enable && npm install -g openclaw@2026.2.26\n\nWORKDIR /app\n\n# 复制本地配置\nCOPY .openclaw /root/.openclaw\n\nEXPOSE 18789\n\nCMD [\"openclaw\", \"gateway\", \"start\"]\n```\n\n然后构建：\n```bash\nmkdir -p /tmp/openclaw-docker\n# 创建上面的 Dockerfile\ndocker build -t openclaw:local -f /tmp/openclaw-docker/Dockerfile /tmp/openclaw-docker\n```\n\n#### 方案C: 等待网络稳定后重试\n```bash\n# 清理并重试\nrm -rf /tmp/openclaw*\ncd /tmp && git clone https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git\ncd openclaw && docker build -t openclaw:local .\n```\n\n### 💡 建议\n鉴于你已经有 OpenClaw 正常运行，**方案B（手动简化 Dockerfile）** 是最可靠的，因为它直接使用你当前的 NPM 安装版本。\n\n需要我帮你创建这个简化版的 Dockerfile 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":76097,"output":456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76553,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772205381218}}
