{"type":"message","id":"8635b56c","parentId":"b19c734c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T15:22:38.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**Docker 服务未运行**，这是导致所有操作失败的根本原因。\n\n### 🔍 问题诊断\n- **Docker 版本已安装**: `20.10.21`\n- **Docker 服务未启动**: `Cannot connect to the Docker daemon`\n\n### 🛠️ 解决步骤\n\n#### 1. 启动 Docker Desktop\n在 macOS 上：\n- 打开 **Applications** → **Docker Desktop**\n- 等待 Docker 完全启动（状态栏图标变为鲸鱼形状）\n\n#### 2. 验证 Docker 服务\n```bash\n# 检查 Docker 是否运行\ndocker info\n\n# 查看 Docker 进程\nps aux | grep docker\n```\n\n#### 3. 拉取官方镜像\n一旦 Docker 服务启动，使用官方镜像：\n```bash\n# 官方推荐的镜像\ndocker pull alpine/openclaw:latest\n\n# 或者 ghcr.io 镜像\ndocker pull ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:latest\n```\n\n### 💡 为什么需要 Docker Desktop\n在 macOS 上，Docker 需要 **Docker Desktop** 应用来提供 Linux 虚拟机环境，因为 Docker 本身是为 Linux 设计的。\n\n请先启动 Docker Desktop 应用，然后我再帮你拉取和构建 OpenClaw 镜像。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":78494,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772205748034}}
