{"type":"message","id":"c9b9adf6","parentId":"19719d19","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:07:52.422Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n### 📡 代理间通信规范详解\n\n#### **核心原则**\n- **身份明确**: 每个代理必须清晰标识自己的身份\n- **通道统一**: 所有代理共享同一个 Telegram 频道\n- **格式标准**: 使用结构化消息格式便于解析\n\n#### **消息前缀规范**\n- **Core Agent**: `## 📊 Core Agent`  \n- **Stock Agent**: `## 📊 Stock Agent`\n- **MCS Agent**: `## 📊 MCS Agent`\n\n#### **通信场景**\n\n**1. 用户请求路由**\n```\n用户 → Core Agent: \"分析我的投资组合\"\nCore Agent → Stock Agent: \"请提供今日投资组合分析\"\nStock Agent → Core Agent: \"## 📊 Stock Agent [投资分析结果]\"\nCore Agent → 用户: 整合后的完整响应\n```\n\n**2. 跨域协作**\n```\nCore Agent → MCS Agent: \"评估这个技术方案的可行性\"\nMCS Agent → Core Agent: \"## 📊 MCS Agent [技术评估报告]\"  \nCore Agent → Stock Agent: \"基于技术评估，调整科技股仓位建议\"\nStock Agent → Core Agent: \"## 📊 Stock Agent [调整后的投资建议]\"\n```\n\n**3. 系统协调**\n```\nCore Agent: \"执行每日备份流程\"\nStock Agent: \"## 📊 Stock Agent [日志已生成]\"\nMCS Agent: \"## 📊 MCS Agent [日志已生成]\"  \nCore Agent: \"## 📊 Core Agent [所有代理日志已备份到GitHub]\"\n```\n\n#### **消息格式标准**\n```json\n{\n  \"from\": \"agent_id\",\n  \"to\": \"agent_id\", \n  \"action\": \"specific_action\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"ISO8601\",\n  \"data\": { \"structured_content\": \"...\" }\n}\n```\n\n#### **错误处理**\n- **超时机制**: 30秒无响应自动重试\n- **降级策略**: 专业代理不可用时，Core Agent 提供基础服务\n- **状态同步**: 定期心跳确保代理在线状态\n\n这个规范确保多代理系统既能**独立运作**，又能**高效协作**，同时保持与用户的清晰沟通。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":83892,"output":486,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772244455628}}
