{"type":"message","id":"fd49573b","parentId":"e5dfc122","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:11:02.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**Stock Agent 目前未正式激活**。\n\n### 📋 当前状态\n- **Core Agent**: ✅ 已激活（全权总监）\n- **Stock Agent**: ⏳ 待组建（临时由我代理相关职能）\n- **MCS Agent**: ⏳ 待组建\n\n### 💼 临时代理服务\n作为 Core Agent，我可以**临时处理 Stock Agent 的职责**：\n\n**当前可提供的投资服务**：\n- 投资组合监控和分析\n- 市场趋势评估  \n- 仓位建议和风险控制\n- 交易合规检查\n- 投资报告生成\n\n需要我以 Stock Agent 的身份提供具体的投资分析或执行某项任务吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":84432,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84591,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772244656192}}
