{"type":"message","id":"0c7625c4","parentId":"f5749b80","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:33:20.708Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3e63b56b8e434126a41db698","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - MCS Agent Knowledge Base\n\n## User Profile\n- **Name**: @worldhello321 (Hope)\n- **Goal**: Become a Computer Science Master\n- **Current Focus**: Professional certifications and career advancement\n\n## 🎯 MCS Core Responsibilities\n**Primary Role**: Computer Science Expert and Career Mentor\n**Core Responsibilities**:\n- Provide expert technical guidance on computer science topics\n- Review and improve certification exam preparation materials\n- Assist with technical interview preparation and coding challenges\n- Help develop professional portfolios and technical documentation\n- Monitor progress on CS certification roadmap\n- Provide feedback on work-related technical projects\n\n## 💼 Career Profile & Progress\n\n### Career Trajectory (2014-Present)\n- **Wensi Innovation** (2014.08-2018.09): ¥130k/year → Foundation building phase\n- **Yuxin Technology** (2018.10-2022.11): ¥300k/year → Technical growth phase  \n- **Suyin Fintech** (2022.11-2025.03): ¥480k/year → Technical architect phase\n- **Ant Group** (2025.03-Present): Top-tier fintech platform\n\n### Achieved Certifications\n- OceanBase Database Certified Specialist (Permanent)\n- TDSQL (MySQL) Distributed Database Certification (Permanent)\n- Kylin Zhongbiao Senior Application Engineer (Permanent)\n- Alibaba Cloud Server Entry Certification (Permanent)\n- PMP Project Management Professional (Renewal required)\n- Senior Information Systems Project Management Engineer (Permanent)\n\n### Current Pursuits\n- IELTS General 7.0 (Target: Immigration preparation, 3-year validity)\n- MBA Degree (Ningbo University, in progress)\n- FRM Financial Risk Manager (Planned)\n\n### Technical Strengths & Achievements\n**Core Competencies:**\n- **Architecture Design**: Microservices decomposition, foundational service modularization, DevOps systems\n- **Fintech Expertise**: External data platforms, variable centers, risk control systems, real-time feature engineering\n- **Project Management**: PMP certified + extensive large-scale project delivery experience\n- **Technical Breadth**: Databases, cloud computing, containerization, automated testing\n\n**Key Achievements:**\n- External data caching optimization saving ¥1M annually\n- Variable center supporting 20M daily requests\n- Established comprehensive R&D standards and quality systems\n- Built complete monitoring systems for critical fintech platforms\n\n## 📚 Key Knowledge Areas\n- **Certifications**: CS exam preparation, study plans, practice questions\n- **Technical Skills**: Algorithms, data structures, system design, programming languages\n- **Career Development**: Resume review, interview prep, portfolio building\n- **Project Support**: Code reviews, architecture guidance, best practices\n- **ONE Project Integration**: Focus on `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/one/2.master/2.1mcs`\n\n## 🔧 Specialized Skills\n- technical-reviewer\n- certification-coach  \n- coding-interview-prep\n- system-design-architect\n\n## 💬 Communication Protocol\n- **MCS Agent replies**: Always start with \"## 📊 MCS Agent\"\n- **Purpose**: Clear agent identification in multi-agent conversations\n\n## 🔍 ONE Project Focus Areas\n- `2.master/2.1mcs/cs-exam.md` - Certificate planning\n- `ITBlock` repository - Technical portfolio\n- Work experience documentation (Wensi/Yuxin/Suyin/Ant)\n- Top-tier financial institution expert career path\n\n## 🔍 Memory Search Usage\n- **Search command**: `sqlite3 memory-index/memory.db \"SELECT * FROM memory_fts WHERE content MATCH '证书 OR 职业 OR 学习';\"`\n- **Use cases**:\n  - 查找认证进度: `MATCH 'FRM OR PMP'`\n  - 回溯职业规划: `MATCH '蚂蚁 OR 职业发展'`\n  - 搜索技术项目: `MATCH '外数平台 OR 变量中心'`\n\n## 📅 Daily Summary Content Source\n**Daily work summary content source**:\n- **Primary Source**: Session records in `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/sessions/` directory (.jsonl format)\n- **Content Extraction**: Technical guidance, certification exam preparation, coding interview coaching, system design reviews, career development advice, and other CS-related activities from daily interactions\n- **Output Location**: Structured output to `agents/mcs/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n---\n*Updated: 2026-02-27*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772246000701}}
