{"type":"message","id":"19d07044","parentId":"ed584000","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:33:55.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n### 🔍 子代理配置分析\n\n**✅ 代理目录结构完整**\n- **Stock Agent**: ✅ 配置完整，包含交易规则、持仓信息、风控设置\n- **MCS Agent**: ✅ 配置完整，包含职业规划、认证进度、技术专长\n\n**⚠️ 关键配置缺失**\n\n#### **1. 缺少多账号 Telegram 配置**\n当前配置只有单个 Telegram bot token：\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"botToken\": \"SINGLE_TOKEN\"  // 只有一个token\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**需要改为多账号配置**：\n```json5\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"core\": { \"botToken\": \"CORE_TOKEN\" },\n        \"stock\": { \"botToken\": \"STOCK_TOKEN\" }, \n        \"mcs\": { \"botToken\": \"MCS_TOKEN\" }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### **2. 缺少路由绑定规则**\n当前没有 `bindings` 配置，所有消息都会路由到默认代理（main/core）。\n\n**需要添加绑定规则**：\n```json5\n{\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"agentId\": \"core\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"core\" } },\n    { \"agentId\": \"stock\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"stock\" } },\n    { \"agentId\": \"mcs\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"mcs\" } }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### **3. 代理列表配置正确**\n```json\n[\n  { \"id\": \"main\", \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace\" },\n  { \"id\": \"stock\", \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\" },\n  { \"id\": \"mcs\", \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/workspace\" }\n]\n```\n✅ 这部分配置正确\n\n### 🛠️ 修复建议\n\n**步骤1**: 为每个代理创建独立的 Telegram bot（通过 BotFather）\n**步骤2**: 更新 `openclaw.json` 添加多账号和绑定配置  \n**步骤3**: 重启 OpenClaw gateway\n\n这样就能实现**三个代理完全独立的 Telegram 通信**，每个代理处理自己的频道消息。\n\n需要我帮你生成完整的修复配置文件吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":93686,"output":548,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94234,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772246016634}}
