{"type":"message","id":"4acfc68c","parentId":"95743a1f","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:38:35.261Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_26b428434a5841d0b460e5de","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig overwrite: /Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 b05a115893fc371f7e2d935c939bca3ce0d7534c15d01fd7a2c6ee15520173b4 -> 4937e88ef5d06c85e3c2bedbf0cadba74c0e3e20703e605e1bdee32af8c9f1e2, backup=/Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated bindings. Restart the gateway to apply."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1452,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig overwrite: /Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 b05a115893fc371f7e2d935c939bca3ce0d7534c15d01fd7a2c6ee15520173b4 -> 4937e88ef5d06c85e3c2bedbf0cadba74c0e3e20703e605e1bdee32af8c9f1e2, backup=/Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated bindings. Restart the gateway to apply.","cwd":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772246315259}}
