{"type":"message","id":"ecc24219","parentId":"c5f560b5","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:41:40.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **多代理配置修复已完成！**\n\n### 🔧 已完成的修复\n1. **Telegram 多账号配置**:\n   - ✅ Core: `8524712381:AAGZd6jnFzvbAxMPa7P1FMejPZsgwBYh8Fw`\n   - ✅ Stock: `8295117727:AAEeoGEQL8B797xWxJVbnImAS4cC_Ut5zwI`  \n   - ✅ MCS: `8616018374:AAF3oGIVLpVZBUYlt7VX9h3hFrqgKxtAPzM`\n\n2. **路由绑定规则**:\n   - ✅ Core → core 账号\n   - ✅ Stock → stock 账号  \n   - ✅ MCS → mcs 账号\n\n3. **Gateway 重启**: ✅ 配置已生效\n\n### 🧪 验证方法\n现在你可以通过以下方式测试：\n\n**1. 发送测试消息到各 bot**:\n- @core_yourname_bot → 应该收到 Core Agent 响应\n- @stock_yourname_bot → 应该收到 Stock Agent 响应  \n- @mcs_yourname_bot → 应该收到 MCS Agent 响应\n\n**2. 检查代理状态**:\n```bash\nopenclaw agents list --bindings\n```\n\n### 🎯 当前状态\n- **Core Agent**: 正常运行，处理主频道消息\n- **Stock Agent**: 已激活，可独立处理投资相关请求\n- **MCS Agent**: 已激活，可独立处理 CS 认证和技术问题\n\n三个代理现在完全独立，各自拥有专属的 Telegram 频道，互不干扰。需要我测试某个特定代理的功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":99184,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772246458496}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecf25614","parentId":"ecc24219","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:44:44.342Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 10:44 GMT+8] 我检查了3个都能通讯，我创建了一个群聊，在群里@机器人，没有回复，看下什么问题，参考官方文档：https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/telegram"}],"timestamp":1772246684339}}
