{"type":"message","id":"e7cba35a","parentId":"3558da83","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:48:52.053Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_62b8a9b1eeb2493bbe486e6f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nChecking channel status…\nGateway reachable.\n- Telegram core: enabled, configured, running, mode:polling, token:config\n- Telegram mcs: enabled, configured, running, in:5m ago, mode:polling, token:config\n- Telegram stock: enabled, configured, running, in:7m ago, mode:polling, token:config\n\nTip: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli#status adds gateway health probes to status output (requires a reachable gateway)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1948,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply 