{"type":"message","id":"46dce0ab","parentId":"e7cba35a","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:49:06.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n### 🔍 群聊配置问题诊断\n\n**发现关键问题**：\n\n#### **1. 缺少群组配置**\n- **当前状态**: `channels.telegram.groups` 未配置\n- **影响**: 由于 `groupPolicy: \"allowlist\"`（默认），**所有群组都被阻止**\n\n#### **2. 隐私模式可能未禁用**\n- 日志显示只有 DM 消息（chat=5520269161）\n- **没有群组消息记录**，说明机器人根本收不到群组消息\n\n### 🛠️ 修复步骤\n\n#### **步骤1: 添加群组全局配置**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.groups '{\"*\": {\"requireMention\": true, \"groupPolicy\": \"open\"}}'\n```\n\n#### **步骤2: 禁用 Privacy Mode**\n- 联系 **@BotFather** \n- 发送 `/setprivacy`\n- 为 **每个机器人**（core/stock/mcs）选择 **\"Disable\"**\n\n#### **步骤3: 重新添加机器人到群组**\n- 从群组中移除所有三个机器人\n- 重新添加它们到群组\n\n#### **步骤4: 重启 Gateway**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 📋 验证清单\n- ✅ 群组配置已添加\n- ✅ Privacy Mode 已禁用  \n- ✅ 机器人已重新添加\n- ✅ Gateway 已重启\n\n需要我帮你执行步骤1（添加群组配置）吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":109298,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772246932053}}
