{"type":"message","id":"cf57acbd","parentId":"2b134829","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:53:15.781Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5dba9c63fdd345e9bafaa368","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig overwrite: /Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 4937e88ef5d06c85e3c2bedbf0cadba74c0e3e20703e605e1bdee32af8c9f1e2 -> 9b72eca9b2be8c425284534df709539b8ad23a7b92587543a594f1fc7af74f6b, backup=/Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated channels.telegram.groups. Restart the gateway to apply."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1642,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├────────────────────────