{"type":"message","id":"86522e07","parentId":"e2ac13a8","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:17:07.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n**没有在日志中找到群组消息记录**，这说明：\n\n### 🔍 可能原因\n1. **Privacy Mode 仍未完全禁用** - 机器人收不到群组消息\n2. **群组ID格式问题** - 需要正确的负数格式\n3. **机器人未正确添加到群组**\n\n### 🛠️ 手动获取群组ID的方法\n\n#### **方法1: 使用 @userinfobot**\n- 在群组中添加 `@userinfobot`\n- 发送 `/start` \n- 它会显示群组ID（格式：`-1001234567890`）\n\n#### **方法2: 检查消息链接**\n- 转发群组消息到私聊\n- 消息链接中包含群组ID\n\n#### **方法3: 直接提供ID**\n如果你知道群组ID，请直接告诉我（格式如 `-1001234567890`）\n\n### ⚡ 临时解决方案\n我可以先配置**通配符路由**，让所有群组消息都能被处理：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set bindings '[{\"agentId\":\"stock\",\"match\":{\"channel\":\"telegram\",\"accountId\":\"stock\"}},{\"agentId\":\"mcs\",\"match\":{\"channel\":\"telegram\",\"accountId\":\"mcs\"}},{\"agentId\":\"main\",\"match\":{\"channel\":\"telegram\",\"accountId\":\"core\"}}]'\n```\n\n这样虽然不够精确，但能确保功能正常。你希望我先用通配符方案吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":121863,"output":338,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122201,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772248608867}}
