{"type":"message","id":"75487251","parentId":"07997969","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:20:58.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **群聊智能路由配置已完成！**\n\n### 🔧 已配置的功能\n- **@stock** → Stock Agent 专属回复\n- **@mcs** → MCS Agent 专属回复  \n- **@core** → Core Agent 专属回复\n- **无@消息** → Core Agent 默认回复\n\n### 🧪 测试方法\n请在 \"one\" 群组中测试以下场景：\n\n1. **@stock_yourname_bot** + 任意消息 → 应该收到 Stock Agent 的投资分析\n2. **@mcs_yourname_bot** + 任意消息 → 应该收到 MCS Agent 的技术指导  \n3. **@core_yourname_bot** + 任意消息 → 应该收到 Core Agent 的综合响应\n4. **直接发送消息**（不@任何人）→ 应该收到 Core Agent 的默认响应\n\n### 📋 配置详情\n- **群组ID**: `-1003661163902`\n- **路由规则**: 精确匹配 + 默认兜底\n- **提及要求**: `requireMention: false`（允许无@消息）\n\n现在你的多代理系统已经完全按照需求配置好了！需要我测试某个特定场景吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":123255,"output":278,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772248844359}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ccec5d6","parentId":"75487251","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:23:00.816Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 11:23 GMT+8] 检查一下，我现在无@时，多个agent都回复我， 我只希望不@时，由core答复我"}],"timestamp":1772248980813}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0113993","parentId":"9ccec5d6","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:23:14.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n### 🔍 问题诊断\n\n**原因**: 所有三个机器人都在同一个群组中，且都配置了 `requireMention: false`，所以它们都能看到所有消息。\n\n### 🛠️ 修复方案\n\n需要为 **Stock** 和 **MCS** 机器人设置 **`requireMention: true`**，只让 **Core** 机器人接收无@消息。\n\n#### **执行修复命令**\n\n```bash\n# 为 Stock 和 MCS 机器人设置 requireMention: true\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.stock.requireMention true\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.mcs.requireMention true\n\n# 确保 Core 机器人保持 requireMention: false\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.core.requireMention false\n```\n\n#### **验证配置**\n```json5\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"core\": { \"requireMention\": false },\n        \"stock\": { \"requireMention\": true },\n        \"mcs\": { \"requireMention\": true }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 📋 预期行为\n- **无@消息**: 只有 Core 机器人响应 ✅\n- **@stock**: Stock 机器人响应 ✅  \n- **@mcs**: MCS 机器人响应 ✅\n- **@core**: Core 机器人响应 ✅\n\n让我立即执行这些修复命令：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3b6624b625794745b446915e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.stock.requireMention true && openclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.mcs.requireMention true && openclaw config set channels.telegram.accounts.core.requireMention false"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":123595,"output":379,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123974,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772248980815}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8cc7660","parentId":"a0113993","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:23:16.408Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3b6624b625794745b446915e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nError: Config validation failed: channels.telegram.accounts.stock: Unrecognized key: \"requireMention\"\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":1861,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nError: Config validation failed: channels.telegram.accounts.stock: Unrecognized key: \"requireMention\"\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","c