{"type":"message","id":"4f9136dd","parentId":"7943edb4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:40:34.504Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_27cb36747ca84761b10ca0d3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig overwrite: /Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 b1c35fae3aa75e68febe346b5d14252b39cd0912284a5b288811c01c07bc963b -> 680dd168473b00591eccb8a0deae90aaa2eeb0ed5e57d24ecd0beb03e3f6d7e6, backup=/Users/hope/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated channels.telegram.groups.-1003661163902. Restart the gateway to apply."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1832,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ───────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                │\n│  Moved channels.telegram single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.telegram.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                                │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├─────────