{"type":"message","id":"d4fc1db3","parentId":"9708698c","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:42:41.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **已回退到安全方案！**\n\n### 🔧 当前配置\n- **群组**: `-1003661163902` 设置为 `requireMention: true`\n- **行为**: **只有 @ 机器人时才会响应**\n- **无@消息**: **没有任何机器人会回复**\n\n### 🎯 预期行为\n现在应该实现：\n\n1. **@stock_yourname_bot** → Stock Agent 回复 ✅\n2. **@mcs_yourname_bot** → MCS Agent 回复 ✅  \n3. **@core_yourname_bot** → Core Agent 回复 ✅\n4. **无@消息** → **没有任何回复** ✅\n\n### 🧪 请测试验证\n在 \"one\" 群组中测试这四种场景，确认是否符合预期。\n\n这个方案虽然不如你最初设想的完美（无@时由 Core 回复），但它是**当前 OpenClaw 版本中最稳定可靠的配置**，避免了多机器人冲突问题。\n\n需要进一步调整吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":144020,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772250152352}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1b6bcdd","parentId":"d4fc1db3","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:46:22.605Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 11:46 GMT+8] 在群组里 core @ 其他agent ，其他agent收不到吗？无法给回复？ 我来@这个agent就可以？看下什么问题？https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/multi-agent"}],"timestamp":1772250382600}}
