{"type":"message","id":"e1956740","parentId":"758f79e0","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:39:35.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **完全 OK！**\n\nCode Agent 已经：\n- ✅ 成功创建并配置\n- ✅ 添加到代理列表中  \n- ✅ Gateway 已重启并激活\n- ✅ 准备接收开源项目分配\n\n现在可以开始使用了！需要分配具体的开源项目吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":163978,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164049,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772257109805}}
