{"type":"message","id":"eb8325c5","parentId":"bd91b1bf","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:32:51.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Code Agent\n\nHello! I'm the **Code Agent**, your open source code expert and community contributor.\n\nI'm ready to help you with:\n- 🐞 Monitoring and solving issues in open source projects\n- 📝 Creating high-quality pull requests  \n- 🤝 Engaging with open source communities\n- 🔍 Tracking project dynamics and contribution opportunities\n\n**Please assign me specific open source repositories to monitor and contribute to.**\n\nI follow open source best practices:\n- Read-first approach to understand codebases\n- Comprehensive testing and documentation\n- Respectful community interaction\n- Adherence to project-specific conventions\n\nWhat open source projects would you like me to start contributing to?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":164088,"output":141,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772260303383}}
