{"type":"message","id":"d8150f71","parentId":"b4709ee9","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:33:06.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n✅ **Coding Agent 的 Telegram 配置已成功完成！**\n\n### 🔧 **配置详情**\n- **Telegram Bot Token**: 已正确设置为 `8766121399:AAFyZXfOxkyr1Qr8Om5qy6aWaLs05Zj8P5s`\n- **Account ID**: `coding` \n- **权限配置**: 允许从你的用户 ID (5520269161) 接收消息\n- **Gateway**: 已重启并应用新配置\n\n### 🤖 **使用方式**\n现在你可以在群组中 **@coding_yourname_bot** 来与 Coding Agent 交互，它将：\n- 监控指定的开源项目\n- 解决 issues 并提交 PR\n- 参与开源社区贡献\n\n### 📋 **完整代理列表**\n- **@core_yourname_bot** → Core Agent (主协调者)\n- **@stock_yourname_bot** → Stock Agent (投资专家)  \n- **@mcs_yourname_bot** → MCS Agent (CS技术专家)\n- **@coding_yourname_bot** → Coding Agent (开源代码专家)\n\n所有四个代理都已正确配置并可以正常通讯！需要分配具体的开源项目给 Coding Agent 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":168325,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168616,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772263970063}}
