{"type":"message","id":"28d8ce89","parentId":"4aa6679a","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:34:44.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Core Agent\n\n我需要先在群组中添加 Coding Agent 才能发送消息。请先：\n\n1. **将 @coding_yourname_bot 添加到 \"one\" 群组中**\n2. **为 Coding 机器人禁用 Privacy Mode**（通过 @BotFather 发送 `/setprivacy` → Disable）\n\n完成后，你就可以直接 **@coding_yourname_bot** 来获取报告了。\n\n或者，如果你希望我直接让 Coding Agent 发送报告到你的私聊，请告诉我，我可以配置它向你发送私信。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":167359,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167479,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772264017838}}
