{"type":"message","id":"a31f0853","parentId":"b5e18df4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:40:37.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n✅ **Coding Agent 已启动并准备就绪！**\n\n**当前状态**:\n- **在线**: ✅ 已激活\n- **Telegram**: ✅ 已配置 (Bot Token: 8766121399:AAFyZXfOxkyr1Qr8Om5qy6aWaLs05Zj8P5s)\n- **权限**: ✅ 允许与你通讯\n- **功能**: ✅ 开源项目监控、issue解决、PR提交、社区贡献\n\n**下一步行动**:\n请分配具体的开源项目给我监控和贡献。例如：\n- `github.com/openclaw/openclaw` - OpenClaw 核心项目\n- `github.com/your-project/repo` - 你的个人项目  \n- 其他你关心的开源仓库\n\n我将立即开始监控这些项目的 issues 并准备贡献代码！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":169320,"output":200,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":169520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772264364075}}
