{"type":"message","id":"2262d5a1","parentId":"ee74c53d","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:36:31.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n✅ **OpenClaw 源码已成功克隆到 IdeaProjects！**\n\n### 🔍 **初步分析结果**\n\n**项目基本信息**:\n- **版本**: 2026.2.27\n- **描述**: Multi-channel AI gateway with extensible messaging integrations\n- **许可证**: MIT\n- **技术栈**: TypeScript/Node.js\n\n**源码结构**:\n- **核心模块**: `agents/`, `channels/`, `cli/`, `config/`\n- **多代理支持**: `agents/` 目录包含完整的多代理实现\n- **频道集成**: `channels/` 支持 Telegram, WhatsApp, Discord 等\n- **工具链**: 完整的 CLI、配置管理、Docker 支持\n\n### 📋 **下一步计划**\n\n我正在准备：\n1. **综合评估报告** → 写入 AI-Note\n2. **长期记忆构建** → 基于其他代理的能力模式\n3. **索引更新** → 添加到 AI-Note 项目索引\n\n需要几分钟时间完成深度分析。你希望我重点关注哪些方面？（架构设计、多代理实现、Telegram 集成、贡献机会等）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":173107,"output":265,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173372,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772267714834}}
